BBC or something but now it's on TV.

00:33:34.740 --> 00:33:36.360
Now it's on the news.

00:33:36.360 --> 00:33:39.680
So people are starting to ask
me, "Hey, didn't you go there?"

00:33:39.680 --> 00:33:40.980
I was like, "Yeah.

00:33:40.980 --> 00:33:43.770
