alter of the hope of my childhood.

00:46:35.730 --> 00:46:40.810
Etchmiadzin's carillon rang out,
calling her children to her.

00:46:40.810 --> 00:46:49.990
I am parting from you with
love, City of Aleppo farewell."

00:46:49.990 --> 00:46:56.230
And, that is the poem for all of us

00:46:56.230 --> 00:47:00.450
